          "text": "Heavy Bombs: Each time the bearer ends a Normal move , you can select one enemy unit it moved over during that move and roll nine D6, adding 1 to each result if that unit is a MONSTER or VEHICLE : for each 5+, that unit suffers 1 mortal wound . Inferno Bombs: Each time the bearer ends a Normal move , you can select one enemy unit it moved over during that move and roll nine D6, adding 1 to each result if that unit is not a MONSTER or VEHICLE : for each 5+, that unit suffers 1 mortal wound ."
